# =============================================================================
# DIGITAL SHADOW - LOCAL DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
# =============================================================================
#
# IMPORTANT:
# 1. Copy this file to .env (NOT .env.local - just .env)
# 2. Fill in your actual credentials
